        body("This product exists within the larger Jacksonville Design Community initiative, which aims to transform Jacksonville from a city of siloed design practitioners into a connected knowledge-sharing ecosystem. The Designer\u2019s Compass addresses the community\u2019s core insight: Jacksonville doesn\u2019t lack talented designers, it lacks the infrastructure to surface, develop, and connect them."),
        body("The tool serves three strategic functions within the community:"),
