        numbered("Knowledge repository entry point: Designers who assess themselves are more likely to seek out resources, mentors, and opportunities through the community.", "numbers"),
        numbered("Talent intelligence layer: Aggregated (anonymized) data about the community\u2019s collective strengths and gaps informs programming decisions, partnership pitches, and advocacy.", "numbers"),

        heading("2.3 Design Principles", HeadingLevel.HEADING_2),
        bullet("Bold, not generic. The visual language should feel like it was designed by designers, not generated by a template. Dark-mode-first aesthetic with vivid accent colors per archetype."),
